-- Agile Property, Hong Kong Builder, Sells $650 Million of Seven-Year Bonds
-- Sarah McDonald
-- 2010-04-21T22:36:59Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-04-21/agile-property-hong-kong-builder-sells-650-million-of-seven-year-bonds.html

          
          
             Agile Property Holdings Ltd., the
Hong-Kong listed developer, sold $650 million of 8.875 percent
notes due in 2017, according to data compiled by Bloomberg.  
 Bank of America Merrill Lynch, Morgan Stanley, Deutsche
Bank AG and Standard Chartered Plc managed the sale, the data
show.  
